{"tid":1433574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽！警世！]再講差佬記者會，我地好快輸！","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T15:34:17.000Z","uid":108757,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"92bb1e46afdd74e8c9002fc8e968716146c21d7f","tid":1433574,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:51:56.000Z","msg":"今個星期開始，差佬日日搞個好柒嘅記者會，結果個個就即刻衝去笑鳩佢，我地呢個運動係笑鳩差佬咩？我地嘅目標係咩呀？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span>呀！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span>呀！<br />\n<br />\n點解個個掛住講差佬個垃圾記者會，無人講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行動、戰略、文宣</span></span>野呀？<br />\n由宜家開始，所有人幫手推<span style=\"color: red;\">行動PO、戰略PO、文宣PO</span>！繼續<span style=\"color: red;\">整連儂牆</span>，繼續<span style=\"color: red;\">派傳單、貼街招</span>呀！<br />\n<br />\n快啲幫手推<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場集會、大埔遊行、深水埗遊行、港島東遊行</span>！無用嘅PO就負皮上一頁，唔好再推！再講差佬記者會，林鄭就會得逞！"},{"pid":"5c527ed1bc473561bde1924203ca7da6e451832d","tid":1433574,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:54:42.000Z","msg":"[行動post 冇人理]未來數日反送中活動簡報<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433511</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11b286c6dbda32cee4cd02fbef7038c7b0508ae","tid":1433574,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"［突發］和你飛 集會無人呀！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431684</a>"},{"pid":"f8b2d973f368fc9f8d85c230ad0977d495c2aad4","tid":1433574,"uid":47509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"h